article.description: — Kaiyem Cleary had 16 points in Le Moyne's 88-57 victory against Stonehill on Thursday night.
article.headline: Cleary helps Le Moyne secure 88-57 victory over Stonehill
article.linkText: Cleary helps Le Moyne secure 88-57 victory over Stonehill
article.story: SOUTH EASTON, Mass. -- — Kaiyem Cleary had 16 points in Le Moyne's 88-57 victory against Stonehill on Thursday night. Cleary had five rebounds for the Dolphins (10-13, 5-4 Northeast Conference). Darrick Jones Jr. scored 15 points and added six rebounds and three steals. Nathan McClure was 4 for 6 from 3-point range, scoring 15. Louie Semona led the way for the Skyhawks (3-22, 1-9) with nine points, six rebounds and four assists. Austin Abrams added nine points, while Thatcher Stone scored eight. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
